config ZEPHLET_SILENT
    bool "Silent zephlet (CoAP functional test fixture)"
    select NANOPB
    select ZBUS
    select ZBUS_ASYNC_LISTENER
    help
      Enable the `silent` zephlet copy used by the CoAP discovery
      functional test. `silent` opts into the CoAP RPC frontend but not
      into discovery, so a `silent_inst` instance is callable yet must
      never appear in `/.well-known/core`. The test asserts that
      asymmetry to prove the `coap_discoverable` proto option gates
      emission.

if ZEPHLET_SILENT

module = ZEPHLET_SILENT
module-str = zlet_silent
source "subsys/logging/Kconfig.template.log_config"

endif
